node.text:
KANSAS CITY PEEPS! The Dude Perfect Tour is coming to your city for an EPIC Halloween show and experience on October 31st! 🎃👻 Get your tickets (link in bio) and come out dressed in your best Halloween costume to see us in person!

We’ll have trick or treating in the concourse, a costume contest with a chance to be a part of the show, games, photo stands, surprises and more. See ya there!
